      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCc09f00b0250110058a848a10427928d2"></a>Removal of the cooling system hoses and unions
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e11444"> </a>Remove the front half-fairings (<a href="77983.html#DUC6b420cf82a8210058217e66c96b901d2">Removing the front half-fairing</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e11449"> </a>Remove the half-fairings (<a href="77987.html#DUC104f7d582a9610058109cc3160c450d2">Removing the tank fairings</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e11454"> </a>Drain the cooling system (<a href="77257.html#DUCf34a5aa829f91005800d816ce97b3fd2">Changing the coolant</a>).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e11460"> </a>Loosen clamps (1) of the water radiator (3) pipe (2) and the clamps that fix the thermostat/radiator sleeve (4) to the thermostat.
         </div>
      </div>
